      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's still got so much life left in her! This car has been super reliable for me and is in really solid shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures. It runs beautifully and has been well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for a dependable vehicle that's ready to hit the road today, you've found it! Come by and take it for a test drive, I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
