      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 22
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333 hp with surgical precision. Mated to a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain provides a visceral, analog connection to the road. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring a documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings to maintain the integrity of its MacPherson strut/multi-link suspension geometry. The factory limited-slip differential remains tight, ensuring optimal power distribution. This example is a true driver\u2019s car, showing light cosmetic patina but excelling in mechanical performance and structural rigidity.",
